name: CQ.Ext.chart.CartesianSeries
doc: CartesianSeries class for the charts widget.

props.name: axis
props.doc: Indicates which axis the series will bind to

props.name: displayName
props.doc: The human-readable name of the series.

props.name: showInLegend
props.doc: False to not show this series in the legend. Defaults to true.

props.name: xField
props.doc:
The field used to access the x-axis value from the items from the data
source.

props.name: yField
props.doc:
The field used to access the y-axis value from the items from the data
source.
